\b Candidate: Public vs Org-linked\b0\par
\bullet  Public candidate: not tied to any org; only the candidate (and Platform Admin read-only) can see them.\par
\bullet  Org-linked candidate: tied to one org; Org Admin / Account Managers / Recruiters can see them per org access rules.\par
\par
\b Invite chains (how users are created)\b0\par
\bullet  Platform Admin \u8594? invites Org Admin (creates organization + sends invite link)\par
\bullet  Org Admin \u8594? invites Account Manager (sends invite link)\par
\bullet  Org Admin and/or Account Manager \u8594? invites Recruiter (sends invite link)\par
\bullet  Candidate \u8594? self-signup (email confirmation may be required)\par
